name: You are matter
description:
Pen+ink+pencil on 300 gsm paper | 2018

My first piece in Lettering series. Made around 2018 with pen+pencil+ink. This piece was initially from #tomorrowneedsyou trend by fellow lettering artist @tarwane (on IG) to support everyone that has a existential crisis. All my fellow artists don't feel small if you're not getting that supports you deserved. In time, you'll getting paid, all your tears & sweats
